=== Etymology ===
From Greek meaning "longhaired star", due to the long tail of comets.

== [[noun]] ==
#heavenly body in [[orbit]] around the sun which as it travels leaves behind a trail of [[ice]] crystals and [[dust]] which are seen as a "tail on a star".

